				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13892068/scp-5345#post-4833987</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 02 Dec 2020 01:37:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Calibri Bold</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5045819</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>There's definitely some potential to the premise here, but the execution didn't really pan out well. 5345 just sort of dumps exposition everywhere, and the whole thing feels almost&#8230; meaningless, I want to say. Like nothing really ends up happening, we just learn 5345's backstory and that's about it. 5345 himself is alright, although his character kind of gets stale after a while. Altogether, while I think there's definitely something to tap into here, it just didn't do it for me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
